# Bring analytics team to party

When the user says **bring analytics team to party**, **add analytics pipeline**, **setup analytics agents**, **onboard analytics workflow**, or **`/bring-analytics-team`** — bootstrap the **Cursor ten-phase agent pipeline** in the **current workspace**. Do not ask for confirmation first.

**This is NOT:** building a GA4 funnel script, ETL, or Python analytics module — unless the user also asks for that work separately.

**This IS:** copy/install `.cursor/commands/` (analysis-intake, data-pull, …), `docs/AGENT_ROLES.md`, handoff templates, and domain doc stubs from [cursor-analytics-pipeline](https://github.com/shaysakal-web/cursor-analytics-pipeline).

